{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act22side", "eventName": "照我以火", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "FC-8", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "她的影子", "storyInfo": "為躲避搜捕，葦草帶著眾人躲入廢墟，隨後意外發現這裡正是傳說中的塔拉王城的遺址。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“我將我的心跡寫入詩韻。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“你啊，將到來的混沌時代中的你。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“會知道我的靈魂是如何將其追尋。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "34_g7_galekingruins", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_242", "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我就知道，他們不會來這堆被天災砸爛的石頭裡面找人。", "name": "塔拉流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "多虧早上起了那麼大的霧，不然我們還沒這麼容易脫身。", "name": "塔拉流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，小心。我們畢竟沒有防護裝備，在這裡受傷的話，是有感染風險的。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_728_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "莫蘭，你也是。源石多發環境，對感染者來說更加危險。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_728_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好，我會注意的。", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#1$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_728_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......凱莉睡著了？", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_728_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是，應該只是睡了，不是昏迷，我能感覺到她的呼吸還很平穩。睡著能讓她少受一些痛苦。", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#1$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_728_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......但我還是怕，再不停下來處理凱莉的傷勢的話，她撐不過去。", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#3$1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_728_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你們，失望嗎？", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_728_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不會的。你不是說過了嗎？我們現在不得不和一些深池士兵戰鬥，是因為他們不想要第二位“領袖”。", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#6$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但他們還有更大的目標，不會一直追捕我們的。", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#6$1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在這樣逃亡的生活，我們也已經習慣了，可以忍耐下去。", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#6$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_728_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過在那之後呢？你還沒有告訴過我們你的想法。", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#1$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_728_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還沒有把握，抱歉。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對了，廢墟深處，也許有源石晶簇少一些的地方，我想去看看，能不能找到一個暫時的藏身處。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_728_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大家都應該停下來休息一下了。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_728_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可那個方向，是不是有人在？", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#1$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_728_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然看上去只是普通人，可我們應該也要躲開。就像你之前說的一樣，這種地方有人出沒，太異常了，一定要小心......", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#3$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_728_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_728_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......不用。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_728_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你看起來很害怕。怎麼了？", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#1$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_728_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒關係，不用擔心我。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（......她來過這裡？在這附近？）", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_242"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎，那邊的人，走路的樣子是不是有些奇怪？", "name": "塔拉流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別看。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_242"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 12.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咿——她怎麼已經——", "name": "塔拉流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$e_skill_ignite_cast", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_magic_1", "volume": 1.0, "delay": 0.7}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.6, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她應該，離世有一段時間了。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是，那種源石技藝操控著這具身體在行動，就像我們之前見到的那些深池士兵一樣。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_728_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼要操縱一個普通人？", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#3$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還不知道。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——跟我走吧，這些被源石技藝控制的死者，我來應對。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_walk_stage"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡光線很暗，沿著石階往下走的時候，小心裸露的碎晶簇......莫蘭，你背著凱莉方便行動嗎？", "name": "葦草"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我沒問題。只要你的火一直燃著，我看得見東西。", "name": "莫蘭"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好。我們儘量往深處走，別發出太大聲音。", "name": "葦草"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——", "name": "葦草"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是......", "name": "莫蘭"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......蓋爾王的王城？"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$calm_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"screenadapt": "showall", "image": "34_g8_galekingruins_inside", "x": 100.0, "y": 0.0, "xScale": 1.3, "yScale": 1.3}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "backgroundTween", "attributes": {"xFrom": 100.0, "yFrom": 0.0, "yTo": 0.0, "xScaleFrom": 1.3, "yScaleFrom": 1.3, "xScaleTo": 1.3, "yScaleTo": 1.3, "duration": 20.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 0.0, "fillfrom": 0.0, "fillto": 0.2, "fadetime": 0.1}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 4.0, "fillfrom": 0.0, "fillto": 0.2, "fadetime": 0.1}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對於那業已覆滅的王朝，有人想像它灰石的骸骨間堆滿死戰不退的將士盔甲，有人聲稱它仍將黃金的王冠藏匿於古老陰森的機關之下。"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有人以現代倫蒂尼姆的高牆去襯托王城的恢弘，以無邊的克拉斯德內海比擬英雄時代美德的興榮，又哀歎它被維多利亞的陰影日漸銷蝕。"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "人們想像這座古城是塔拉悲情的墓碑，怨恨的亡魂。"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "34_g8_galekingruins_inside", "screenadapt": "showall", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 0.0, "fillfrom": 0.2, "fillto": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 4.0, "fillfrom": 0.2, "fillto": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但它只是安靜地坐在山丘上，袒露出此地未有王城時的核心。"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "生出野草，爬滿藤蔓。"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_242"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這得是多久以前的東西了？五百年？一千年？", "name": "塔拉流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_728_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "噓......不要把凱莉吵醒了。", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#1$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_242"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉......我只是有點驚訝，不對，太驚訝了。", "name": "塔拉流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說真的，雖然我們年年演的戲目都會講不同的蓋爾王故事，我也知道我們是塔拉王國子民的後代，所以被叫做塔拉人......", "name": "塔拉流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_728_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......但以前沒有人相信，這一切竟然真的存在。", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#1$1"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_728_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "甚至還有傳說裡，熔融了所有塔拉戰士的武器、顛覆了王朝命運的熔爐......", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#3$1"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_728_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......很久以前，我遇到過一個四處尋找吟遊詩人的城裡人。", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#1$1"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他對我說過，傳說雖然有許多是後人編造，但那些故事裡，一定留下了歷史的痕跡。", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#1$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_728_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#11$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "葦草，你一定知道很多，是不是？", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#1$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_728_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#11$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_728_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#11$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不喜歡這裡嗎？我們進來後，你就一直不說話。", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#4$1"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_728_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......或許是吧。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很小的時候，我就經常讀著塔拉的傳奇故事，直到入睡。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為維多利亞王室寫作的人也好，想要留存塔拉文明的人也好，他們總是寫，“德拉克的天性是爭鬥”。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "傳說最初率領蓋爾氏族的德拉克，燒乾河水向南而行，逃離互相廝殺爭奪王座的族親，開拓了塔拉的土地。"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "傳說維多利亞的紅龍殺死了塔拉最後一位遊牧的德拉克首領，給他牙牙學語的幼子安上蓋爾王的頭銜。"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "傳說塔拉的德拉克自此囚於宮廷，哪怕“放逐王”拋下王冠行走荒野二十年，歸來覲見時仍被在位的至親殺害。"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#13$1"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "塔拉的歷史，充滿了這樣的故事。德拉克的王城裡，遍佈陰謀與鮮血。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#13$1"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "比起憧憬和幻想，我......害怕這裡。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我害怕，有朝一日，要與我的姐姐爭鬥。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......不過，天災留下的晶簇，這裡幾乎看不見。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在這裡休息，應該是安全的。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_242"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那就好。來，莫蘭，我幫你把凱莉放下。", "name": "塔拉流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_728_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓她躺在這邊吧，背風的地方。", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#6$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡的牆很堅實，位置也很隱蔽，我們即使在晚上生起火，應該也不會被外面的人注意到。", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#6$1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_242"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎，葦草她怎麼——", "name": "塔拉流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_728_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓她自己去那邊看看吧。", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#6$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "34_g8_galekingruins_inside", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$ghosthunter_intro", "key": "$ghosthunter_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“我放下戰士的榮譽，只為以後塔拉的土地不必再被鮮血浸泡，德拉克的同族不必再刀劍相向。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“除非有朝一日，紅龍的火焰能令死去的戰士從熔爐中復生。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_cloakmovement", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "葦草聽見輕微的響動。"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她收回了想要觸摸眼前生鏽設備的手。"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它是......活著的？", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_226_weed_1#7", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 0.8, "duration": 1.0, "end": "true"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它只不過是，誰都可以驅動的東西......有人把它重新點燃了，你為什麼要覺得奇怪？", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_226_weed_1#7"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......嗯，她來過了，不奇怪。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "透過孔隙，她看到了紫色的火焰。"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡是曾經的王城，她一定會來......也一定會發出嘲笑聲吧？傳說中的君王，留下的東西，就只是這些而已。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡燃起了她的火焰，所以附近才會有那麼多不得安息的死者。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那只是，在附近迷路渴死的流浪者，無緣無故地被死亡的火焰喚起。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_226_weed_1#1", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 0.8, "duration": 0.0, "end": "true"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不......別靠近。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_226_weed_1#1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你也害怕那簇火吧？", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_226_weed_1#1"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_226_weed_1#1", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 0.8, "duration": 0.0, "end": "true"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我看得到，你想熄滅它。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_226_weed_1#1"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......嗯，它會給許多人帶去痛苦。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_226_weed_1#1", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 0.8, "duration": 0.0, "end": "true"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可你真要這麼做的話，我不會讓你過去。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_226_weed_1#1"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她點燃了深池的火。你知道，你沒辦法再燃起同樣的火焰。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_226_weed_1#1"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她做了很多壞事，說了很多漂亮的謊言，可是，那些是非做不可的。她號召了成千上萬的塔拉人跟隨，不挑剔聖人或暴徒，貴族或賤民。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_226_weed_1#1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_226_weed_1#7", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 0.8, "duration": 0.0, "end": "true"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些，你做不到。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_226_weed_1#7"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不......我做得到。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不信，那些犧牲都是必要的，也絕不會相信，塔拉人要得救，只有她的那一種方法可行。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_226_weed_1#1", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 0.8, "duration": 0.0, "end": "true"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是從很早以前，從橡林郡的那場大火開始，她就已經是領袖。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_226_weed_1#1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她想起那個趴在街道上傷痕累累的女孩。自己想拉起她，讓她快走，卻又害怕自己向她伸手的話，她也會變成一堆灰燼。"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "姐姐走到了她身邊。"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你想活下去嗎？姐姐問道。"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你旁邊就是下水道。從那裡爬下去，那些可惡的貴族就再也追不上你。"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蔓德拉。她從那裡逃出來，最終又回到那裡。"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_226_weed_1#1", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 0.8, "duration": 0.0, "end": "true"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而你，你終究沒有伸手拉起任何人。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_226_weed_1#1"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，如果我能夠向她伸出手，也許，事情會變得不一樣。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果她真的得救，那她本該知道，除了像那天的縱火者那樣，擁有為非作歹的權力......她還有許多路可以走。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 279, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_226_weed_1#1", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 0.8, "duration": 0.0, "end": "true"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可實際上，你連自己的力量都害怕，只能讓別人來操縱它。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_226_weed_1#1"}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......所以，連姐姐都對你失望了，更不用說其他人。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_226_weed_1#1"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......不，你這麼說，不對。你說的都是已經過去的事。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在的我，已經握住過他人的手了。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不能說，是我拉起了他們，但他們想要前行的話，我的火，可以燒出道路。哪怕那條路，是他們牽著我走。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她......如果她能看到這一切，她不會失望的。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_226_weed_1#1", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 0.8, "duration": 0.0, "end": "true"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你只是，偶然有了同伴。", "name": "“領袖”"}, "figure_art": "avg_226_weed_1#1"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在他們面前，你表現得能戰鬥、演說、號召大家......你假裝自己有力。", "name": "“領袖”"}, "figure_art": "avg_226_weed_1#1"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可你其實只是在模仿她。", "name": "“領袖”"}, "figure_art": "avg_226_weed_1#1"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你只能，成為她的影子。任何手段，她都可以用到極致，而你比她，多出來太多猶豫和軟弱。", "name": "“領袖”"}, "figure_art": "avg_226_weed_1#1"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "21_G5_victoria_street_n_ruins", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "keep": "true", "initamount": 0.0, "amount": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她想起那些縱火燒毀塔拉人街區的軍官。他們放聲嘲笑塔拉人的自以為是，嘲笑幾乎不識字的塔拉人竟然抗議橡林郡的法令不公。"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她知道，這就是姐姐最後對老師說的，將會發生的事情。"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維多利亞人親手點燃了仇恨的火焰。在燒光一切之前，這場大火不會停下。"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別眨眼，姐姐對她說，看清我們的生活是如何一次又一次地被毀去。"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在遍地焦黑屍骸中間，掌控死亡之火的德拉克抬手施術。"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "冰涼的紫火蓋過了原本灼燒著死者的烈焰。"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其實那死亡的火焰幾乎從來沒有取走過任何生命。她只是准許他們從灰燼中爬起，在死後得以向燒毀他們家園的人復仇。"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "34_g8_galekingruins_inside", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "keep": "true", "initamount": 0.0, "amount": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我不後悔。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "過去，我一直覺得她是對的。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“為了最終建成塔拉人理想的國度，我們的生命都可以作為燃料，投入火中......”", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 323, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在她身邊，我一直是這麼說的。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 324, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......可燃料燒盡之後，她的國度裡，還剩下誰？", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我猶豫過，反思過，逃避過......", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 327, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不後悔。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我逃到了這裡，見過了她看不到的人與事。我想說的，一定與她不同。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，我也不會再害怕想起她。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 331, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我絕不會......困在自己的影子裡！", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 333, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_226_weed_1#7", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 0.8, "duration": 0.0, "end": "true"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "認出這座王城時，你不是正在害怕嗎？", "name": "“領袖”"}, "figure_art": "avg_226_weed_1#7"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想，你無法回答你的“同伴”你們將去哪裡，但心裡早已備好答案。", "name": "“領袖”"}, "figure_art": "avg_226_weed_1#7"}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不變成我的話，你在深池的夢想裡，要如何找到自己的位置呢？", "name": "“領袖”"}, "figure_art": "avg_226_weed_1#7"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_humanchange", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_npc_722_1#1$1", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 0.8, "duration": 1.0, "end": "true"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——拉芙希妮，你想要什麼呢？", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_722_1#1$1"}, {"id": 342, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "21_G6_decisivebattlealley_n", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "keep": "true", "initamount": 0.0, "amount": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$burningloop1", "volume": 0.7, "loop": "true", "channel": "fire"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_deathburning", "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 2.0, "amount": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "葦草想起那場大火裡走向她們的死者。"}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_226_weed_1#2"}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......快停下......", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_226_weed_1#2"}, {"id": 358, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們傷痕累累，面目全非，眼中卻仍然燃燒著渴望。"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們完成了對維多利亞軍官的復仇，走向為他們燃起火焰的人。"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_226_weed_1#2"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不要再向前走了......", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_226_weed_1#2"}, {"id": 365, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_226_weed_1#1"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們應該......得到安息！", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_226_weed_1#1"}, {"id": 367, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.03, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 12.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_burn", "layer": 2.0}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "bgEffect", "attributes": {"layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$e_skill_ignite_cast", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$b_char_fireharm", "volume": 0.6, "delay": 0.4}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.8, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——反應過來的時候，離她最近的人已經倒在她的面前，空洞的眼眶注視著她。"}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在她自己一閃而過的熾烈火光之中，死亡的火焰熄滅了。"}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_226_weed_1#2"}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......對不起，姐姐。對不起......", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_226_weed_1#2"}, {"id": 384, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我，不是有意破壞你的法術......", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": 